SearchState - Enum in ca.mcgill.ecse211.enumeration
Enumeration for the searching state This class is used to keep track of the robot state: In_Progress means that the rings hasnt been found yet, the robot is till searching Time_out means the robot is taking a lot of time to find the rings Ring_found state is set when the rings have been collected from the tree
